graph TB
    subgraph "Observability"
        Logs[Logs<br/>What happened?<br/>Structured JSON events]
        Metrics[Metrics<br/>How much?<br/>Counters, gauges, histograms]
        Traces[Traces<br/>Where did time go?<br/>Distributed request path]
    end

    Logs --> ELK[ELK / Loki]
    Metrics --> Prom[Prometheus + Grafana]
    Traces --> Jaeger[Jaeger / Tempo]

    Alert[Alerting] --> Metrics
    Alert --> Logs
    Dashboard[Dashboards] --> Metrics
    Dashboard --> Traces
